    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 6 headline and caption accompanying article about groups of police officers who ride motorcyles off duty</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A headline and caption yesterday with an article about groups of police officers who ride motorcyles off duty described the groups incorrectly in some editions. The groups, which include the Wild Pigs and Blue Knights, are motorcycle clubs for law enforcement officers, not ''gangs.''</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>A headline and caption yesterday with an article about groups of police officers who ride motorcyles off duty described the groups incorrectly in some editions. The groups, which include the Wild Pigs and Blue Knights, are motorcycle clubs for law enforcement officers, not ''gangs.''</p>
